<div class="quoteContent">
<div class="bq_fq bq_fq_lrg qt-fnt bq-smpl-qt">
<p class="b-qt qt_413483">The beauty of a woman is not in a facial mode but the true beauty in a woman is reflected in her soul. It is the caring that she lovingly gives the passion that she shows. The beauty of a woman grows with the passing years.</p>
<p class="bq_fq_a">
<a href="/authors/audrey-hepburn-quotes" class="qa_413483 oncl_a">Audrey Hepburn</a>
</p>
</div>
