<div id="pos_1_9" class="grid-item qb clearfix bqQt">
<a href="/quotes/audrey_hepburn_394356" class="b-qt qt_394356 oncl_q" title="view quote">
<div style="display: flex;justify-content: space-between">
I love people who make me laugh. I honestly think it&#39;s the thing I like most, to laugh. It cures a multitude of ills. It&#39;s probably the most important thing in a person.
<img src="/st/img/4889785/fa/chv-r.svg" alt="Share this Quote" class="bq-qb-chv">
</div>
</a>
<a href="/authors/audrey-hepburn-quotes" class="bq-aut qa_394356 oncl_a" title="view author">Audrey Hepburn</a>
